Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Crimson Web
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a spider web-patterned hydrographic over a red base coat and finished with a semi-gloss topcoat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Be careful where you walk, you never know where the web is spread

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Urban Masked
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using a tangle of masking tape as a stencil.
Rare Special Items.lore: True power is demonstrated with subtle application

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Forest DDPAT
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a Digital Disruptive Pattern (DDPAT) hydrographic.
Rare Special Items.lore: By the time you're close enough to notice the pixels it's already too late

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Stained
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been given a forced patina using lemon and mustard dripped onto the surface.
Rare Special Items.lore: If you think it's messy now, wait until you see it under a blacklight

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Boreal Forest
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a forest camouflage hydrographic.
Rare Special Items.lore: The woods can be a dangerous place... never travel alone

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Slaughter
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted in a zebra-stripe pattern with aluminum and chrome paints with various reflectivities, and has then been covered with a tomato red candy coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Valeria doesn't pay Javier to ask questions... she pays him to pry out answers

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Scorched
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted in a sun-dappled pattern.
Rare Special Items.lore: The Phoenix is not a symbol of destruction... it's a symbol of rebirth - Valeria Jenner, Revolutionary

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Safari Mesh
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using mesh fencing and cardboard cutouts as stencils.
Rare Special Items.lore: A predator is a predator, no matter the environment

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Night
Rare Special Items.desc: It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a night ops color scheme.
Rare Special Items.lore: It's the whisper of the wind... it's the bite at your neck

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Case Hardened
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been color case-hardened through the application of wood charcoal at high temperatures.
Rare Special Items.lore: A little color never hurt anyone

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Blue Steel
Rare Special Items.lore: This is the malbec of weapon design - Booth, Arms Dealer

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Huntsman Knife | Fade
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted by airbrushing transparent paints that fade together over a chrome base coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: This isn't just a weapon, it's a conversation piece - Imogen, Arms Dealer In Training

Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted using a combination of subtly patterned hydrographics and dry-transfer decals of wings.
Restricted Skins.lore: Sometimes the wings of an angel don't mean salvation

Restricted Skins.name: MAC-10 | Tatter
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a high-tech design reminiscent of flames.

Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted using a combination of hydrographics and dry-transfer decals to create the look of a wood stock and gold inlay.
Restricted Skins.lore: With age comes wisdom and stopping power

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Galil AR | Kami
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a hydrographic in a Japanese manga pattern.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: P2000 | Pulse

Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Striking colors for a striking weapon
